OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The tale of a man who says he floated  
OL,6, in the sea for more than a day to      
OL,7, survive the tsunami which hit Tonga has
OL,8, captured global media attention.       
OL,10,FThe volcanic eruption and tsunami hit  
OL,11,Fthe island nation on Saturday, sweeping
OL,12,FAtata local Lisala Folau out to sea.   
OL,14,FMr Folau told the BBC that he held on  
OL,15,Fto a floating log during his 27-hour   
OL,16,Fordeal at sea, before finally reaching 
OL,17,Fthe shore again.                       
OL,19,FTonga has confirmed three deaths though
OL,20,Fthe extent of damage is still unknown. 
